Experience Faster Salesforce CRM Connector Refreshes

With the support of stream processing, data stream deployment and change events are optimized to process data with minimal latency. Stream processing is available for standard objects, such as Account, Contact, Lead, and Opportunity, and all custom objects.

Where: This change applies to Data Cloud in Developer, Enterprise, Performance, and Unlimited editions.

When: This functionality is available starting in June 2024.
